  {
    "key": "071b65a1b86ac63aaaaa4ecb1f4f1c8843118f68e3835c658c8fb84d8a7964f1",
    "original": "There's something different about this character. Physically they seem unchanged, yet somehow a sense of dread precedes them. Any harm that they endure, on or off the battlefield, seems to affect another nearby. Useful in a fight, annoying in camp, and surely isolating in every day society.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "getDescription = function getDescription(){\n    return \"There's something different about this character. Physically they seem unchanged, yet somehow a sense of dread precedes them. Any harm that they endure, on or off the battlefield, seems to affect another nearby. Useful in a fight, annoying in camp, and surely isolating in every day society.\";;\n    return;\n}"
